OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784564342
OL,3,CWoman escapes injury after house and
OL,4,Ccar targeted in Armagh arson attack
OL,6,FPolice are investigating an arson
OL,7,Fattack in Armagh in the early hours of
OL,8,FSunday morning.
OL,10,FA house and a car were set on fire in
OL,11,Fthe Mullacreevie Green area of the
OL,12,Fcity at around 2.30am.
OL,14,FThe Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService extinguished the blazes.
OL,17,FPolice said a woman was in the house
OL,18,Fat the time of the incident but was
OL,19,Fnot injured.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
