OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784564342
OL,3,CWoman escapes injury after house and
OL,4,Ccar targeted in Armagh arson attack
OL,6,FThe PSNI said: "The car was completely
OL,7,Fburnt out and damage was caused to the
OL,8,Ffront of the house."
OL,10,FIt added: "Inquiries are ongoing and
OL,11,Fdetectives would appeal to anyone who
OL,12,Fsaw anything or who has any
OL,13,Finformation, including dash-cam, CCTV
OL,14,For other footage, to contact them on
OL,15,F101, quoting reference number 203 19/
OL,16,F07/26."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
